<s> I was told AltaVista had released a super-lean search service, along the lines of google.  </s>
<s> So I tried it.  </s>
<s> Annd this is what I got: We're sorry.  </s>
<s> Raging.com does not support text-only browsers.  </s>
<s> For a superior text-only search, please visit [link]AltaVista.  </s>
<s> I faked my user agent string, and got a perfectly usable (nice, clean, simple) search engine.  </s>
